        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 22 at 3:28AM CDT by NWS Corpus Christi TX</headline>
        <description>Patchy to areas of fog have developed across portions of the
Coastal Plains this morning. Expect visibilities generally 1 to 3
miles with a few locations seeing visibilities 1/4 mile or less
at times.

Use caution if traveling as visibility may change rapidly
in a short amount of time. Use low beam headlights and leave
extra distance between your vehicle and others on the road.
</description>
